-- ============================================================================
-- TEST I: bitset_max_density_multi GUC override → linear at low K/N
-- ============================================================================
-- K=40 on ts_multi (K/N = 0.004, default-admitted at 1/200) goes to linear
-- when the multi gate is forced to 0.
